name: Openshift nginx cartridge
body:
### The Openshift nginx cartridge
The openshift nginx cartridge provides a way to run nginx on [www.openshift.com](https://www.openshift.com/).

The goal of this cartridge is to provide a simple and quick way to install and use nginx, so lets [get started](/getting-started)
